{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20/comments/38997871.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20#comment-38997871"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 20, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{1dfbdd30-34c5-4b09-82ef-9bfe2917877b}ts=1533303"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-common", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-common", "uuid": "{1dfbdd30-34c5-4b09-82ef-9bfe2917877b}"}, "title": "Console_TEST creates a bunch of garbage directories in the home directory"}, "content": {"raw": "@iche033 has a trick where cmake creates a header with a macro containing path to the build directory. `Console_TEST` could import that header and create the randomly named directories in that path.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>@iche033 has a trick where cmake creates a header with a macro containing path to the build directory. <code>Console_TEST</code> could import that header and create the randomly named directories in that path.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-09T21:28:53.122517+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Shane Loretz", "uuid": "{656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:684383ab-ac95-4859-a350-4a6f41a94a22/c7a1ebf5-cade-4115-9f26-9d3facb776db/128"}}, "nickname": "Shane Loretz", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:684383ab-ac95-4859-a350-4a6f41a94a22"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38997871}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20/comments/38997933.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20#comment-38997933"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 20, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{1dfbdd30-34c5-4b09-82ef-9bfe2917877b}ts=1533303"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-common", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-common", "uuid": "{1dfbdd30-34c5-4b09-82ef-9bfe2917877b}"}, "title": "Console_TEST creates a bunch of garbage directories in the home directory"}, "content": {"raw": "Pull request #60 addresses this issue.\n\nThe culprit was the file logger, which makes its logging directories relative to the home directory. I've tweaked the tests to funnel all the test log files into a `~/tmp-ign/` directory.\n\nEdit: I also have it clear the directories once the tests are finished so we don't endlessly pollute the file system.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p><a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pull-requests/60/cleanup-log-directories-after-tests-are\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">Pull request #60</a> addresses this issue.</p>\n<p>The culprit was the file logger, which makes its logging directories relative to the home directory. I've tweaked the tests to funnel all the test log files into a <code>~/tmp-ign/</code> directory.</p>\n<p>Edit: I also have it clear the directories once the tests are finished so we don't endlessly pollute the file system.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-09T21:32:10.272769+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": "2017-08-09T21:32:57.599957+00:00", "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38997933}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20/comments/39787431.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20#comment-39787431"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/issues/20.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 20, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{1dfbdd30-34c5-4b09-82ef-9bfe2917877b}ts=1533303"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-common", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-common", "uuid": "{1dfbdd30-34c5-4b09-82ef-9bfe2917877b}"}, "title": "Console_TEST creates a bunch of garbage directories in the home directory"}, "content": {"raw": "pull request #60", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p><a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pull-requests/60/cleanup-log-directories-after-tests-are\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #60</a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-09-11T23:50:55.805139+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.